{"search_data": "Central Pradhan Mantri Ujjwala Yojana \u2013 Free LPG Connection for Women \u0939\u093f\u0902\u0926\u0940 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u092a\u0922\u093c\u0947\u0902According the estimates, about 1.50 Crore BPL families will be benefited under the scheme in the year 2016-17. The scheme will cover 3.5 Crore more BPL families in the next two years. The scheme provides a financial support of Rs 1600 for each LPG connection to the BPL households.The identification of the BPL beneficiaries will be made in consultation with the state governments and union territories. This is the first ever welfare scheme by the Ministry of Petroleum and Natural Gas which would benefit crores of women belonging to the poorest households.Table of Contents  Objective of Pradhan Mantri Ujjwala YojanaHow to Apply for Pradhan Mantri Ujjwala YojanaEligibility CriteriaDocuments RequiredNeed for Pradhan Mantri Ujjwala YojanaOperational Details of Pradhan Mantri Ujjwala YojanaUjjwala Yojana AdvertisementObjective of Pradhan Mantri Ujjwala YojanaThe government aims to not just distribute free LPG connections but also reduce the serious health hazards associated with cooking based on fossil fuels. The objective of the scheme is to empower women and protect their health. The scheme is also expected to provide employment to rural youth in supply chain of the cooking gas.How to Apply for Pradhan Mantri Ujjwala YojanaThe applications for the Ujjwala Yojana will be invited through only the offline mode. The interested applicants can apply for the scheme by filling up the prescribed Ujjwala Yojana application form.The application forms of Pradhan Mantri Ujjwala Yojana are available at all the LPG outlets or distribution centers across the country. The interested candidates can obtain the application forms for free or download from the link below.Application form for Pradhan Mantri Ujjwala YojanaView detailed step by step application procedure of Pradhan Mantri Ujjwala Yojana.Eligibility CriteriaBasic eligibility criteria for the Ujjwala Yojana is as followingThe applicant should be a women with minimum age of 18 years as on 01 May 2016.The applicant should belong to BPL (Below Poverty Line) household in the country.The applicant details will be matched to the SECC-2011 data (Rural).The applicant\u2019s household should not already own a LPG connection.Documents RequiredThere are certain documents required to be attached with the application form as below.BPL Certificate Authorised by Panchayat Pradhan / Municipality Chairman*BPL Ration Card*One Photo ID (Aadhar Card or Voter ID Card)*One Recent Passport Size Photograph*Aadhar CardDriving LicenseLease AgreementVoter ID CardTelephone / Electricity / Water BillCopy of PassportSelf-Declaration attested by Gazetted OfficerRation CardFlat Allotment / Possession LetterHouse Registration DocumentsLIC PolicyBank / Credit Card Statement*Mandatory documents.It is not necessary to submit all the above said documents but some of those which can verify your permanent residence address and you as a BPL candidate.Need for Pradhan Mantri Ujjwala YojanaPoor have limited access to Clean fuel (LPG) . LPG spread predominantly in Urban and Semi Urban areas.Use of fossil fuels and conventional fuel like cowdung has a serious health implications for women and Children.According to WHO, 5 Lakhs die every year due to heart disease, pulmonary diseases etc.Indoor air pollution is also responsible for significant number of acute respiratory diseases in young children.Operational Details of Pradhan Mantri Ujjwala Yojana5 Cr LPG connections will be provided to BPL families with a support of Rs 1600 each household.Connections will be given in the name of Women beneficiaries.Identification of BPL families will be made in consultation with State Governments and Union territories.EMI Facility for meeting the cost of Stove and Refill cost.The detailed guidelines of Pradhan Mantri Ujjwala Yojana have been released by the ministry of Petroleum and Natural Gas, the PDF document can be downloaded from the below link. http://www.petroleum.nic.in/docs/UJJWALA.pdfUjjwala Yojana AdvertisementPradhan Mantri Ujjwala Yojana Advertisement\u0939\u093f\u0902\u0926\u0940 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u092a\u095d\u0947\u0902: \u092a\u094d\u0930\u0927\u093e\u0928 \u092e\u0902\u0924\u094d\u0930\u0940 \u0909\u091c\u094d\u091c\u094d\u0935\u0932\u093e \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e \u0939\u093f\u0902\u0926\u0940 \u092e\u0947\u0902.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}